    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Community and Stakeholder Orientation \r\n    Mobile Outreach Camp; \r\n    Hands on coaching of health care providers during mobile clinics \r\n    Strengthening of referral system between mobile health clinics and hospitals \r\n    Training of formal and informal health care providers \r\n    Skilled Birth Attendants (SBA) training for district health staff \r\n    Provision of essential obstetric drugs and equipment for training\r\n    Development of advocacy and health education materials\r\n    Conducting advocacy campaign on health care and education \r\n    Production of an Information Education Communication (IEC) and Behaviour Change Communication (BCC) package for media \r\n    Reintegration of school children through provision of EFA scholarships [arranged by Women's Federation with technical support from Women Development Office \r\n    Provision of out of school adolescent girls with literacy classes through the \"Choose Your Future\" development course (12 day course on RH and literacy) \r\n    Provision Adolescent girls (out of school) with Life Skills education \r\n    Provision of out-of-school adolescent girls with skills development and Livelihood opportunities \r\n    Sensitization/ training workshops for public service personnel and NGO staff on the prevention of and attention of abuse, violence against women and early marriage \r\n    Establishment of  networking with the Para-legal committees \r\n    Development of IEC materials for prevention of and attention to interfamily violence and abuses."
      },
      "ne": null
